ygData.messageBody:
(This isn't mine - I just found it in my archives)

A Black Burrow Lullaby

Muffin sings "When we were just new puppies"
Muffin sings "Fallen from on high"
Muffin sings "Our nanny Gnoll would bark us"
Muffin sings "A Black Burrow Lullaby"
Muffin sings "She'd tell us to sleep quietly"
Muffin sings "Upon our straw lined beds"
Muffin sings "Though adventurers ran all around"
Muffin sings "Scalping Gnollish Heads!"
Muffin sings "to just ignore these madmen"
Muffin sings "Running through our room"
Muffin sings "Turning our quiet burrow"
Muffin sings "Into a giant tomb!"
Muffin sings "She said "no matter all the siblings"
Muffin sings "You will see be slain"
Muffin sings "You will get revenge on all those fools"
Muffin sings "Once you learn to TRAIN!"
